profile.summary:
An enterprising strategic FullStack recruiter, a true partner to business, data & metric driven approach & passionate about cherry picking the right people for the right role in a hyper competitive environment. Expertise in hiring tech and product professionals in a short span of time who can build applications that touch and enrich lives of millions. 

In the last 7 years, I have had the opportunity to navigate the space and gain expertise around Talent Planning & Development, Sourcing, Industry benchmarking, Branding, Candidate Engagement, Diversity & Inclusion, Leadership Hiring while working with CTO-CIO-Product Heads and Campus Recruitment from Tier I-TierII colleges in India. 

A result oriented & methodical approach along with a continuous spree for learning and self-development with an interest towards building an employer brand that helps attract and leverage relevant talents has helped me to start from ground zero in a tech product organization and today we stand at 300+ employees at our APAC Tech Hub, delivering globally a Network for Greater Good in the field of HealthTech.

experience.description:
I joined Tracelink in Jule 2019 and we were building out the APAC R&D center from ground zero. From 1 employee to 300+ now, two things kept me motivated always, one: I was so grateful for being a part of building out this amazing team in India [Engineering/ Product/ Product Design (UI/UX)/ Analytics/ Cloud (AWS)/ Campus(FTE and Intern)] & two: I had the support of my TA team, my Managers, my stakeholders, my Leadership team, without whom I would have never been able to balance my personal and professional life. I can cherish my success as well as failure here.Tracelink's culture is imbibed by each employee and we have always embedded people first in all fronts.

I encourage you to apply and be a part of the amazing culture.
connect at sghosh@tracelink.com
experience.title: Principal Recruiter, APAC- Engineering, Product & Design

experience.description:
I am a part of a Global Talent Acquisition team at Tracelink

Roles & Responsibilities include:
# Building short & mid-term sourcing strategies & executing near term recruitment plans along with engagement to bring the best talent to each role.
# Create & execute a comprehensive hiring plan, analysing requirements to determine target profile needs and closest match.
# Analyse & build JD’s together with the hiring managers and thereby establish hiring strategy & criteria amongst the available target pool. 
# Collaborate closely with hiring managers throughout the recruiting process to ensure we hit their hiring needs and goals
# Leading end to end planning to execution by engaging with hiring managers & key stakeholders 
# Manage talent planning, sourcing and development of Engineering, Analytics, Product and Design, Cloud(AWS) and IT division of Tracelink.
# Partnering with leadership to establish Tracelink as a recognizable “employer of choice” in India and APAC market.
# Serve as the talent advisor and subject matter expert (SME) in hiring for Tracelink APAC.
# Strong Global stakeholder management & Partnerships with internal leadership and executive teams
# Direct sourcing across junior, middle level and senior Director & VP roles in Cloud (AWS), IT, Analytics, Engineering and Product organization.
# Managing end to end campus (Graduate and interns) hiring in India.
# Contributing to the growth of the Tracelink recruiting function by proactively developing and refining the processes, serving as a thought partner for the rest of the team and provide coaching and training as needed.
